      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "NOTHING I WANT (1) form this prep has been excellent and she made it two from two when successful at her latest appearance over 1800m at this track, getting home by 2.75 metres as the favourite when she led all of the way. Likely to get all the favours from this nice draw. Won't find this any harder and she can take care of this line-up. STAR OF PATRICK (6) ran third last start at this track over 1800m, beaten 5 metres when well supported. Expected to run well. HAYOAK (4) has to come into calculations on the back of some strong recent form, most recently when third at this track over 1800m. Has won seven of her eight career runs at this track and must be included in exotic bets. THE VICARS GIRL (7) was in the money two starts ago then things went wrong last start when she broke and finished 40 metres away in fourth over 2230m at this track after racing three-wide without cover at the bell. I Meets a similar line up so if she behaves a big run is likely.",
